page.title: 02What I like about Frogmore.
page.content:
{ What I like about Frogmore.}
I live in Frogmore. There is an estuary and a village shop. I like going for walks along the fields with my family and my dog. The village shop sells things you need and you can buy stamps and post your letters. I like the estuary, you can go for walks and there are paths leading to the fields. The house which is joined on to ours is my grandma and grandad's. There isn't much room to ride your bikes, some people ride on the road and others ride them in their gardens. Sometimes people move into the house next door for their holidays or to wait until their house they are going to buy is ready. I like living in Frogmore, I have lots of friends there and my grandma and grandad live there.
